WEBVTT


00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:45.120
How long has Choi Moon-koo been gone?

00:01:45.479 --> 00:01:46.800
They should still be at the gate.

00:01:55.759 --> 00:01:56.880
Excuse me.

00:02:00.720 --> 00:02:02.760
Madam, what else can I do for you?

00:02:03.040 --> 00:02:04.240
I’m flattered.

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:07.920
I didn't entertain you well last night.

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:09.720
I'm really sorry.

00:02:09.720 --> 00:02:11.880
I'm here to see you off.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.040
No.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:14.960
You’re welcome.

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:17.200
Any news about Miss Shangguan?

00:02:17.480 --> 00:02:20.520
This is why I came to you.

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:24.079
You said you would help me find my daughter.

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:27.040
I refused your kindness.

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:30.200
I didn't know what's good for me.

00:02:30.440 --> 00:02:31.760
I want to ask you

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:33.280
what you said yesterday

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:35.040
Does it still count today?

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.280
Of course.

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:39.560
I'll do my best.

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:42.280
Brigade Commander Cui has always been straightforward.

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:44.040
Please forgive me.

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:45.360
Guards!

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:50.079
Remove their guns.

00:02:55.600 --> 00:02:57.079
What do you mean?

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:59.360
Shangguan Ying was caught in Shanzhou.

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:01.800
How did you know?

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:03.640
You shot us.

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:06.640
I think our army offended you.

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:09.160
Based on the time Ms. Shangguan went missing,

00:03:09.160 --> 00:03:12.000
the longest distance we can go is Shanzhou.

00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:14.960
Other than Brigade Commander Cui's independent Brigade in Shanzhou,

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:16.880
is Zhang Gongyan's 16th Division.

00:03:16.880 --> 00:03:18.280
Brigade Commander Cui is on the mountain.

00:03:18.280 --> 00:03:19.880
It must be Zhang Gong Yan.

00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:21.280
Exactly.

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:23.640
Do you know

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:27.280
what we should do next?

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:32.840
You want to exchange us for Shangguan Eagle?

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:36.000
Major Cai is really smart.

00:03:36.160 --> 00:03:38.320
But Madam,

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:41.360
Zhang Gong Yan is a man of his word.

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:42.520
and greedy.

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:45.000
If you take both of us,

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:46.920
it'll look like a deal.

00:03:47.240 --> 00:03:48.800
It's easy to get caught.

00:03:49.200 --> 00:03:51.280
It takes a lot of effort

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:52.840
at the same time.

00:03:53.200 --> 00:03:55.640
Why don't you let me stay in the fortress?

00:03:56.079 --> 00:03:56.200
No.72 Brigade, Cui...

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:59.040
Let Zhang Gong Yan throw the rat away.

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:01.560
We'll be worried about you.

00:04:02.840 --> 00:04:05.200
Major Chae is right.

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:08.560
I'll leave it to you then.

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:11.920
Jang Gong-yeon.

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:29.040
Young Master.

00:04:30.200 --> 00:04:31.080
Open the door.

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:42.040
What happened?

00:04:42.520 --> 00:04:43.760
This is my arrangement.

00:04:43.760 --> 00:04:44.760
Your arrangement

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:49.560
is to put yourself in prison.

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:51.600
Have you forgotten?

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:53.440
Connect Shangguan Bao.

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:55.360
You're the lead. I'll take over.

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:57.080
If you don't do this,

00:04:57.080 --> 00:04:58.720
you won't be able to separate with Choi Moon-Kui.

00:04:58.960 --> 00:04:59.920
If I don't leave him,

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:02.040
I won't have a chance to see Shangguan Bao alone.

00:05:02.440 --> 00:05:03.440
So,

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:05.920
the superiors will contact Shangguan Bao?

00:05:07.520 --> 00:05:08.720
Great!

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:11.520
I can finally complete my mission.

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:13.200
I can go back to the base

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:15.400
in the base.

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:17.240
Calm down.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.000
The war situation is complicated now.

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:22.320
Even after the reorganization,

00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:24.720
you still have a lot of work to do.

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:30.120
Master Xi.

00:05:32.840 --> 00:05:35.120
Bao, Master asked me to look after Cai Zhen.

00:05:35.320 --> 00:05:36.520
Don't worry.

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:38.840
Keep an eye on her.

00:06:10.600 --> 00:06:11.360
Shangguan Bao.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:13.840
You're so stubborn.

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:16.320
You took my men and threatened me.

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:17.960
You don't want your daughter anymore?

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:20.200
You're the one who's unkind.

00:06:21.400 --> 00:06:23.320
Don't blame me for being ruthless.

00:06:23.320 --> 00:06:26.320
I want to know if a Brigade Commander

00:06:26.320 --> 00:06:28.480
for my daughter's life.

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:30.120
Don't try to threaten me.

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:34.560
I, Jang Gong-yeon,

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:36.120
I won't be threatened or tempted.

00:06:37.880 --> 00:06:40.400
I won't change him.

00:06:40.640 --> 00:06:43.400
Your daughter must be executed.

00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:45.640
Brigade Commander Cui.

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:47.920
In order to complete the law,

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:51.200
you have to sacrifice yourself for the country.

00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:52.320
I will report to the war zone

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:54.360
and give you a reward.

00:06:55.840 --> 00:06:59.400
Since you've decided to kill my daughter,

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:03.480
Brigade Commander Cui is useless.

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:07.280
I'll kill him now.

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:22.280
Jang Gong-yeon.

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:27.760
Jang Gong-yeon!

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:29.560
Are you crazy?

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:32.520
Let me tell you.

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:35.320
You're using your power for personal gains.

00:07:35.320 --> 00:07:36.680
for personal revenge.

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:37.400
If

00:07:37.400 --> 00:07:39.040
the First Minister Command Center finds out,

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:41.560
You know they will punish you severely.

00:07:56.880 --> 00:08:01.000
I always respect the anti-Japanese heroes.

00:08:01.280 --> 00:08:02.280
Excuse me.

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:12.280
Madam, if that’s the case,

00:08:12.880 --> 00:08:14.040
think carefully.

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:16.040
You have no chips.

00:08:18.320 --> 00:08:19.480
I have my own way.

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:31.640
Don't move.

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:33.880
Stay still.

00:09:36.040 --> 00:09:37.480
Don't move.

00:09:37.840 --> 00:09:38.720
Don't move.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:41.440
This way. Hurry.

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:47.000
Who is this?

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:48.800
It’s late. What’s the noise?

00:09:54.280 --> 00:09:55.480
Bad news, Division Commander.

00:09:56.160 --> 00:09:56.880
What’s wrong?

00:09:57.080 --> 00:09:57.920
Shangguan Bao is here.

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:00.480
Hang on!

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:01.320
Yes.

00:10:04.840 --> 00:10:05.960
Hurry, Young Lady.

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:07.920
Untie me. Yes.

00:10:20.680 --> 00:10:21.360
Father.

00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:24.360
Eagle, are you okay?

00:10:24.520 --> 00:10:25.280
I'm fine.

00:10:39.280 --> 00:10:40.080
Go back.

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.920
If you're in danger, protect yourself.

00:11:03.080 --> 00:11:03.720
Wait.

00:11:05.080 --> 00:11:06.120
Aren't you afraid that I'll run away?

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:06.920
I trust you.

00:11:07.040 --> 00:11:09.120
Otherwise, you wouldn't have saved me in Shaanxi.

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:10.000
Fine.

00:11:10.520 --> 00:11:11.520
Give me a gun.

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:13.160
Don’t worry.

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:15.200
I won’t leave Qinglong Camp before I finish my work.

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:21.880
Let’s go.

00:11:34.680 --> 00:11:35.400
Big guy.

00:11:35.560 --> 00:11:36.800
Take the villagers to the Hall of Gathering Elegance.

00:11:37.200 --> 00:11:39.120
Okay, folks, follow me.

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:40.720
Folks, follow me.

00:11:41.040 --> 00:11:42.400
Come with me.

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:43.440
Hurry up.

00:11:58.680 --> 00:11:59.520
Get in.

00:12:18.680 --> 00:12:19.800
That's him.

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:22.200
He also said

00:12:22.360 --> 00:12:23.480
if you don't obey him,

00:12:24.280 --> 00:12:25.320
he will kill me.

00:12:26.160 --> 00:12:27.080
Boss.

00:12:27.560 --> 00:12:28.640
It’s a misunderstanding.

00:12:30.520 --> 00:12:31.920
It’s a misunderstanding, boss.

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:34.800
Please spare my life.

00:12:35.720 --> 00:12:36.800
Please spare my life.

00:12:37.760 --> 00:12:39.320
When you wanted to kill Eagle,

00:12:40.720 --> 00:12:42.320
Do you know what you did wrong?

00:12:46.480 --> 00:12:47.360
Boss.

00:12:47.360 --> 00:12:49.800
Madam, he can’t die.

00:12:50.200 --> 00:12:51.440
If you cut him,

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:53.560
Qinglong Camp will be our enemy.

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:55.080
and fell into war.

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:57.160
I know what you're talking about.

00:12:57.680 --> 00:13:00.160
Since you caught Jang Gong-yeon,

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:02.360
I'll give you face.

00:13:02.600 --> 00:13:05.040
You’d better stay out of this.

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:06.680
Boss.

00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:09.520
Leader.

00:13:11.240 --> 00:13:13.640
He’s responsible for the command of the 16th Division.

00:13:14.080 --> 00:13:15.360
If he dies,

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:19.160
the defense of the whole city will be in vain.

00:13:19.680 --> 00:13:21.080
I'm not pleading for him.

00:13:21.080 --> 00:13:22.840
I'm pleading for the people

00:13:23.480 --> 00:13:24.560
for the people of Shaanxi.

00:13:24.760 --> 00:13:27.120
Boss, I also fight against the Japanese.

00:13:27.440 --> 00:13:30.000
Father, we can’t let him go.

00:13:36.080 --> 00:13:37.920
Boss.

00:13:38.480 --> 00:13:39.480
Boss.

00:13:49.520 --> 00:13:51.760
I’ll teach you a lesson today.

00:13:52.280 --> 00:13:55.400
If you dare to do evil again,

00:13:55.680 --> 00:13:58.920
this knife is the best gift for you.

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:01.640
Thank you. Thank you for not killing me.

00:14:01.960 --> 00:14:03.680
Thank you.

00:14:03.880 --> 00:14:04.800
Madam, thank you.

00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:06.000
On my way here,

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:07.320
my men told me

00:14:07.320 --> 00:14:08.800
there was a fire at Qinglong Fortress.

00:14:09.200 --> 00:14:10.040
Father.

00:14:14.320 --> 00:14:14.960
Let's go.

00:14:15.160 --> 00:14:16.600
Let's go.

00:15:04.280 --> 00:15:06.440
He's not dead. He's just in a coma.

00:15:13.360 --> 00:15:14.280
Where is that?

00:15:14.440 --> 00:15:15.200
It’s the Hall of Gathering Elegance.

00:15:15.560 --> 00:15:16.880
Oh no. Master He and his family

00:15:16.880 --> 00:15:17.920
They are all there. Let’s go.

00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:23.000
Hurry!

00:15:25.800 --> 00:15:27.320
Fall back! Fall back!

00:15:27.840 --> 00:15:28.480
Hurry!

00:15:31.280 --> 00:15:32.880
Baoni. Baoni.

00:15:33.080 --> 00:15:34.000
Hurry up, sweetie.

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:38.240
Let's go.

00:15:41.640 --> 00:15:42.560
Brothers, let's go.

00:15:51.240 --> 00:15:53.680
Baoni. Baoni.

00:15:57.560 --> 00:15:59.680
Let's go, sweetie. Get up.

00:16:00.240 --> 00:16:01.000
Hurry.

00:16:01.680 --> 00:16:02.480
Hurry.

00:16:37.800 --> 00:16:39.360
Mr. He, it’s too dangerous here.

00:16:39.360 --> 00:16:40.880
Take everyone away. I'll cover you.

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:42.000
Thank you, Miss Cai.

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:43.080
Let's go.

00:16:43.080 --> 00:16:44.360
Hurry up.

00:16:44.600 --> 00:16:45.840
Let's go.

00:16:46.360 --> 00:16:47.520
Let's go.

00:16:48.520 --> 00:16:49.840
Guys, hurry up.

00:16:49.880 --> 00:16:50.920
Let's go.

00:16:51.120 --> 00:16:52.120
Hurry up.

00:16:52.160 --> 00:16:53.440
Hurry up, guys.

00:16:53.560 --> 00:16:54.480
Go.

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:01.800
Wait. Let's go.

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:06.520
Let's go.

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:08.760
Hurry up.

00:17:08.920 --> 00:17:09.720
What's going on?

00:17:09.920 --> 00:17:11.440
Brother, it’s good that you’re back.

00:17:11.800 --> 00:17:12.880
The enemy attacked Qinglong Fortress.

00:17:13.119 --> 00:17:14.359
and killed many of us.

00:17:17.160 --> 00:17:18.079
If Chae Jin and Air

00:17:18.079 --> 00:17:18.920
came in time,

00:17:19.240 --> 00:17:20.119
the consequences will be unimaginable.

00:17:20.119 --> 00:17:20.760
Stop talking.

00:17:20.760 --> 00:17:22.280
Take some men to hide there.

00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:23.520
Let's go.

00:17:23.560 --> 00:17:24.880
Hurry up.

00:17:24.880 --> 00:17:25.839
Hurry up.

00:17:25.839 --> 00:17:27.040
The rest of you, follow me.

00:17:32.200 --> 00:17:32.760
Let's go.

00:17:32.840 --> 00:17:34.080
Are you hurt? No.

00:17:34.760 --> 00:17:35.640
Let's go.

00:19:21.320 --> 00:19:22.720
It's too dangerous today.

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:24.560
I thought our family

00:19:24.560 --> 00:19:26.360
almost died in the gathering hall.

00:19:26.560 --> 00:19:27.800
The enemy is too fierce.

00:19:27.800 --> 00:19:29.040
and the fortress was caught off guard.

00:19:30.960 --> 00:19:33.080
We should thank Cai Zhen.

00:19:33.440 --> 00:19:35.160
She really saved our family.

00:19:35.160 --> 00:19:36.240
Of course.

00:19:41.360 --> 00:19:42.080
Baoni.

00:19:45.480 --> 00:19:46.240
No!

00:19:47.520 --> 00:19:48.440
Baoni.

00:19:49.680 --> 00:19:50.600
What's wrong, sweetie?

00:19:51.120 --> 00:19:51.920
Mother.

00:19:54.800 --> 00:19:55.640
Mother.

00:19:55.800 --> 00:19:57.040
It's okay. It's okay, sweetie.

00:19:57.240 --> 00:19:58.680
I want to save her.

00:19:59.240 --> 00:20:00.840
Baoni, I can't save her.

00:20:01.560 --> 00:20:03.320
Nini, I can't save her.

00:20:03.560 --> 00:20:04.640
It's okay. It's okay.

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:05.240
Nini, it's okay.

00:20:05.280 --> 00:20:06.760
Baoni, stop thinking about it.

00:20:07.120 --> 00:20:08.160
It's over.

00:20:12.120 --> 00:20:14.040
Thank you for saving me.

00:20:14.360 --> 00:20:17.200
That's why the villagers survived.

00:20:17.680 --> 00:20:20.760
I took Miss Cai as a hostage before.

00:20:21.280 --> 00:20:22.400
How embarrassing.

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:24.000
You’re welcome.

00:20:24.440 --> 00:20:26.440
It’s the duty of a soldier.

00:20:26.440 --> 00:20:28.720
Besides, I didn't do it alone.

00:20:28.720 --> 00:20:29.880
We have Brother Xi.

00:20:31.960 --> 00:20:33.120
In your opinion,

00:20:33.680 --> 00:20:35.520
who ordered these masked men?

00:20:35.840 --> 00:20:36.800
Japanese.

00:20:37.360 --> 00:20:39.040
Why are you so sure?

00:20:39.640 --> 00:20:41.040
Isn’t it obvious?

00:20:41.800 --> 00:20:45.120
Communist Party would never do such a thing.

00:20:45.720 --> 00:20:48.120
Choi Moon-Kui's independent Brigade wouldn't have done that.

00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:51.880
Jang Gong-yeon can do it in public if he wants revenge.

00:20:52.080 --> 00:20:54.160
Only the Japanese

00:20:54.800 --> 00:20:57.480
do such shameful things.

00:20:57.880 --> 00:21:00.480
But why did the Japanese

00:21:00.480 --> 00:21:02.000
to attack Qinglong Camp?

00:21:02.000 --> 00:21:03.840
Will there be a bigger conspiracy next?

00:21:04.080 --> 00:21:06.200
You should be prepared.

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:10.600
Do you know what they are afraid of?

00:21:11.000 --> 00:21:12.560
They are afraid of

00:21:12.560 --> 00:21:15.520
I stood up and joined forces with the army to fight Japan.

00:21:16.520 --> 00:21:17.720
They don't know.

00:21:18.040 --> 00:21:21.240
But this kind of behavior made me decide.

00:21:21.440 --> 00:21:22.400
Make up your mind?

00:21:23.680 --> 00:21:24.640
Brother.

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:29.040
Miss Cai.

00:21:29.320 --> 00:21:32.160
Thank goodness you arrived in time during the battle at the Hall of Gathering Elegance.

00:21:32.280 --> 00:21:33.800
and saved my family.

00:21:34.120 --> 00:21:38.440
I will never forget your kindness.

00:21:38.880 --> 00:21:40.240
Mr. He, you're too kind.

00:21:40.600 --> 00:21:42.400
How is Ni?

00:21:43.800 --> 00:21:44.800
She's asleep.

00:21:45.640 --> 00:21:46.680
Scared

00:21:46.880 --> 00:21:48.840
He hasn't said a word till now.

00:21:50.200 --> 00:21:52.880
If you need anything, you can ask the military doctor to help.

00:21:53.560 --> 00:21:54.960
Thank you, Major Chae.

00:21:55.200 --> 00:21:56.520
Sit down and talk.

00:22:03.720 --> 00:22:07.360
Miss Cai, if there's nothing else,

00:22:07.680 --> 00:22:09.720
I have a favour to ask.

00:22:10.840 --> 00:22:13.040
Stay here for a few more days.

00:22:13.200 --> 00:22:14.320
Give me a chance

00:22:14.560 --> 00:22:17.480
to treat Miss Cai again

00:22:18.040 --> 00:22:20.880
to make up for my offence.

00:22:22.440 --> 00:22:24.000
Thank you, Madam.

00:22:24.400 --> 00:22:27.000
Thank you.

00:22:27.440 --> 00:22:28.680
That's great.

00:22:29.000 --> 00:22:32.240
Stay with Miss Cai these days.

00:22:32.560 --> 00:22:33.640
Pass my order.

00:22:33.840 --> 00:22:35.680
Miss Cai is my distinguished guest.

00:22:36.000 --> 00:22:37.240
No one can neglect her.

