Meixiang.

00:39:40.640 --> 00:39:41.640
What’s wrong, Master?

00:39:42.480 --> 00:39:43.800
Your aunt and Ni are missing.

00:39:43.960 --> 00:39:45.560
Min Ja and Ni might have gone out.

00:39:46.000 --> 00:39:46.920
Guards!

00:39:49.760 --> 00:39:51.120
Mr. He, what can I do for you?

00:39:51.560 --> 00:39:52.680
Where are your aunt and Ni?

00:39:52.840 --> 00:39:54.200
They went to the city to see a doctor.

00:39:54.360 --> 00:39:55.840
Don't worry. We'll follow them.

00:39:56.240 --> 00:39:57.480
Min Ja and Ni are treating patients.

00:39:57.680 --> 00:39:59.040
There's no need to rush, Master.

00:40:00.440 --> 00:40:01.800
It’s chaotic now.

00:40:02.400 --> 00:40:04.080
Even our Qinglong Fortress is heavily guarded

00:40:04.080 --> 00:40:05.040
were ambushed.

00:40:05.880 --> 00:40:07.400
These two women are outside.

00:40:08.160 --> 00:40:09.400
How can I not worry?

00:40:09.600 --> 00:40:10.440
Let's go and have a look.

00:40:22.360 --> 00:40:23.400
Did you see it clearly?

00:40:23.600 --> 00:40:24.680
Yes.

00:40:25.240 --> 00:40:26.600
They both went in.

00:40:27.040 --> 00:40:28.480
But the most troublesome thing is

00:40:28.760 --> 00:40:30.480
there's a bandit behind.

00:40:42.920 --> 00:40:44.800
Sister, don't be afraid.

00:40:45.360 --> 00:40:47.400
The child is just a little shocked

00:40:47.760 --> 00:40:49.240
and caught a cold.

00:40:49.240 --> 00:40:51.160
No problem. Don't worry.

00:40:51.480 --> 00:40:52.960
I feel much relieved

00:40:52.960 --> 00:40:54.160
I feel much relieved.

00:40:56.960 --> 00:40:58.760
Take these medicines back.

00:40:59.120 --> 00:40:59.960
Remember.

00:41:00.160 --> 00:41:02.240
Make three bowls of water into a bowl of water.

00:41:02.480 --> 00:41:03.400
Once a day.

00:41:03.960 --> 00:41:04.920
Okay.

00:41:05.960 --> 00:41:07.840
Okay, thank you, Dr Fei.

00:41:08.040 --> 00:41:08.880
You're welcome.

00:41:09.080 --> 00:41:10.160
Since we're in the city,

00:41:10.160 --> 00:41:12.120
take your kid around

00:41:12.120 --> 00:41:13.840
Buy something the kids like

00:41:14.240 --> 00:41:15.440
When the child is happy,

00:41:15.600 --> 00:41:17.080
he will recover.

00:41:17.560 --> 00:41:19.440
Yes, you're right.

00:41:19.640 --> 00:41:20.360
Nini, let's go.

00:41:20.560 --> 00:41:21.920
Let's buy something nice.

00:41:21.920 --> 00:41:23.360
Mother, thank you, Dr Fei.

00:41:23.600 --> 00:41:24.360
Let me take it.

00:41:24.640 --> 00:41:26.000
You're still sick, Nini.

00:41:26.000 --> 00:41:27.000
Let me take it. It's okay.

00:41:27.000 --> 00:41:28.440
Nini, pay the bill.

00:41:28.440 --> 00:41:29.720
Thank you, Dr Fei.

00:41:30.640 --> 00:41:31.360
Nini,

00:41:32.480 --> 00:41:34.280
What do you want for fun?

00:41:35.040 --> 00:41:36.960
Didn't you want a red-haired rope last time?

00:41:38.520 --> 00:41:40.160
Go to the rouge shop. I'll buy it for you.

00:41:40.160 --> 00:41:41.640
Mother, forget it.

00:41:41.840 --> 00:41:43.080
I don't want to go.

00:41:43.360 --> 00:41:44.360
Let's go back.

00:41:44.840 --> 00:41:46.240
Come on, they are out.

00:41:46.240 --> 00:41:48.960
Why are you going back? Candied haws.

00:41:49.200 --> 00:41:50.680
I'll buy you candied haws.

00:41:54.760 --> 00:41:55.720
Let's eat together.

00:41:56.600 --> 00:41:57.320
Here.

00:41:57.800 --> 00:41:59.600
Take the medicine back and get the car ready.

00:41:59.800 --> 00:42:01.040
Okay, let's go later. Okay.

00:42:01.040 --> 00:42:02.120
Let's go.

00:42:14.240 --> 00:42:15.560
They've been walking for a while.

00:42:24.760 --> 00:42:25.680
Both of them

00:42:25.880 --> 00:42:27.320
Why don't you go back after taking the medicine?

00:42:27.320 --> 00:42:28.360
Why are you walking around?

00:42:28.720 --> 00:42:29.680
Master.

00:42:29.680 --> 00:42:31.680
Min Ja and Ni have brothers following them.

00:42:31.680 --> 00:42:33.040
Why are you so anxious?

00:42:33.280 --> 00:42:34.520
Nini is still sick.

00:42:35.360 --> 00:42:36.760
